 # tc c a dev lo parent 1: classid 1:100 htb \
 > rate 95Mbit ceil 100Mbit burst 64k
 [...]
 # tc f a dev lo parent 1: protocol arp basic classid 1:100
 [...]
 # tc q a dev lo parent 1:100 handle 100: pfifo_fast
 [...]
 # tc q d dev lo root

